00:02:34,040 --> 00:02:35,040
That's right.
没错。

62
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:37,880
So this is called making a reservation.
所以这就叫“做预订”。

63
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:38,880
So it goes together.
所以它们是搭配使用的。

64
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:43,800
You call to make a reservation or you want to make a reservation.
你打电话“做预订”，或者你想“做预订”。

65
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:44,800
That's right.
没错。

